  m_Name: Slide_09_TheCycle
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  title: The Cycle
  body: "Raid. Kill. Survive. Extract. Die, and you lose it all. Every swing, every
    parry, every decision matters. There are no second chances on the battlefield.
    \n\nGather fuel, navigate to the Temple and defeat the AI overlord. Now draw
    your blade."
  clip: {fileID: 32900000, guid: f1dc4fc1744de40e292efadcc0af3c04, type: 3}
